Community Sourced Capital is an awesome new startup in Seattle that enables people to invest directly in local small businesses. These investments are returned in full (with no interest however), but the benefit is that the small business presumably grew and added jobs! My brother is participating in this with his business, North St Bags. Check out his campaign here <https://www.communitysourcedcapital.com/squareholder/campaigns/a-stitch-in-time-saves-nine> or learn more about the CSC here <https://www.communitysourcedcapital.com/aboutus>
